long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The DID Wallet Decentralized Wallet plug-in is an official DID Wallet implementation that lets you manage your digital identity and assets from within the browser extension. DID Wallet supports ArcBlock's blockchain and Ethereum ecosystem and plans to support more blockchain networks. DID Wallet is also focusing more on DID technology, allowing you to have a digital identity that you can control.
